    "description": "Join the Airtel India family as a Backend Developer in Indore. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Airtel India:\nAirtel India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Go\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Referral bonus program\n• Flexible working hours\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Airtel India!",
